---
// TODO: conectar con Supabase tabla feed
---
<section aria-labelledby="news-heading">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2 id="news-heading" class="section-title">Noticias y actualizaciones</h2>
    <a href="/noticias" class="view-all">Ver todas</a>
  </div>
  <div class="news-list">

    <div class="news-item">
      <div class="news-date">
        <span class="date-day">26</span>
        <span class="date-month">JUN</span>
      </div>
      <div class="news-body">
        <div class="news-icon" style="background: var(--naranja-bg)" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accion)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="7" width="9" height="14"/>
            <rect x="13" y="3" width="9" height="18"/>
            <line x1="2" y1="21" x2="22" y2="21"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="news-title">Nuevo centro de acopio abierto en Guarenas</p>
          <p class="news-desc">Más capacidad para atender mascotas en la zona central.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="news-badge new-badge">Nuevo</span>
    </div>

    <div class="news-item">
      <div class="news-date">
        <span class="date-day">26</span>
        <span class="date-month">JUN</span>
      </div>
      <div class="news-body">
        <div class="news-icon" style="background: var(--arena)" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--marron)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 003 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0021 16z"/>
            <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="news-title">Llegó donación de alimento y medicinas</p>
          <p class="news-desc">Gracias a todos los que hicieron posible esta ayuda.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="news-badge new-badge">Nuevo</span>
    </div>

    <div class="news-item">
      <div class="news-date">
        <span class="date-day">25</span>
        <span class="date-month">JUN</span>
      </div>
      <div class="news-body">
        <div class="news-icon" style="background: var(--azul-bg)" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--azul)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="news-title">Se suman 10 nuevos veterinarios voluntarios</p>
          <p class="news-desc">El equipo sigue creciendo para atender más mascotas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-item">
      <div class="news-date">
        <span class="date-day">25</span>
        <span class="date-month">JUN</span>
      </div>
      <div class="news-body">
        <div class="news-icon" style="background: var(--arena)" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--marron)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="news-title">Plataforma Protege Colitas en operación</p>
          <p class="news-desc">Lanzada 24 horas después del terremoto del 25 de junio.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.section-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--texto);
  margin: 0;
}
.view-all {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--accion);
  text-decoration: none;
}
.view-all:hover { color: var(--accion-hover); }

.news-list {
  background: var(--card);
  border-radius: 1rem;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  overflow: hidden;
}
.news-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  padding: 1rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #F3EDE6;
  transition: background .15s;
}
.news-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.news-item:hover { background: var(--fondo); }

.news-date {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 40px;
}
.date-day {
  font-family: 'Nunito', 'Inter', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  color: var(--marron);
  line-height: 1;
}
.date-month {
  font-size: 0.6875rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--accion);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}
.news-body {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.news-icon {
  width: 24px;
  height: 24px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.news-title {
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--texto);
  line-height: 1.3;
  margin: 0 0 2px;
}
.news-desc {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--texto-sec);
  margin: 0;
}
.news-badge {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-size: 0.6875rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 9999px;
  align-self: flex-start;
}
.new-badge {
  background: var(--verde-bg);
  color: var(--verde);
  border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
}
</style>
